Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply put, this combination of elements could allow us to cyberform entire worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.41,0:00:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... why do I feel a Shockwave plan coming on?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kah... oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.93,0:00:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do not think for a moment, Starscream.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.01,0:00:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That it has gone Unnoticed that you left me at the mercy of the Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.89,0:00:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aah. Master? Are you going to allow one lieutenant to harm another?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.40,0:00:34.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.89,0:00:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.57,0:00:45.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am tempted to force you to share my perception of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.07,0:00:51.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I only did what I thought was best for the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.25,0:00:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I do feel compelled to add that it was my very error
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.91,0:00:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in judgment that made this happy accident possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.75,0:01:07.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I recollect, you were seeking to purge your laboratory of sensitive materials before the Autobots arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.89,0:01:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.54,0:01:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your argument... is logical.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.53,0:01:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exemplary teamwork. Now tell me, Shockwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.47,0:01:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why does this cyber-matter resemble chaos?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.21,0:01:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The basic elements are apparently unstable,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.57,0:01:30.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will turn my attention to correcting that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:37.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... nevertheless, should we use this cyber-matter to restore Cybertron,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.93,0:01:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or cyberform earth, we would require a launch mechanism, would we not?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.15,0:01:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we will focus all our remaining resources
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.15,0:01:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,upon the successful reconstruction of the Omega Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.80,0:02:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}I've done everything I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.01,0:02:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}Considering the limitations of my equipment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.39,0:02:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and less than ideal spare parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.03,0:03:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}It remains uncertain if Ultra Magnus's new appendage will be fit for battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.86,0:03:07.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}though it should prove functional,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}after the requisite amount of therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}That is all we can hope for, old friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.10,0:03:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}You doing okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.45,0:03:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(192,280)}I'm still two-fisted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.62,0:03:20.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So's Magnus.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait and see, the claw's gonna become his signature...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, like the way you own that voice box Ratchet slapped in your throat!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.37,0:03:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you know, everyone understands you fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.19,0:03:36.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you even consider getting it fixed now, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.24,0:03:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, what'd he say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bee's kind of still attached to the sound of his own voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.43,0:03:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His original one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.07,0:03:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look at the bright, shiny side,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Magnus and Jackie single-handedly put the kibosh on project Predacon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though at least one beast that we know of remains...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.72,0:04:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who has demonstrated the ability to transform.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.00,0:04:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Predaking, we will soon plot our strike against the Autobots,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:14.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to punish them for the massacre of your kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.74,0:04:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While I fully intend to exact my revenge,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Project Predacon was merely a squadron,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.63,0:04:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,not an army.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.49,0:04:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.69,0:04:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My liege, if you truly aspire to restore our home world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.26,0:04:35.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I have every faith that you will resurrect the entirety of the Predacon race
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.49,0:04:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the remains which lie there,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.93,0:04:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that I may lead them against any and all of our shared enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We salvaged much of the wreckage of the Omega Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.23,0:04:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the damage was quite severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.27,0:04:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would urge the selective use of earth technology,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.15,0:05:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Retro-fitting its operating systems will be more efficient than rebuilding from scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then do provide Starscream with your wish list.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.93,0:05:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since Shockwave must turn his attention to the stabilization of our Cyber-matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you will be in charge of acquisitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.70,0:05:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime! We have trouble brewing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:24.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cons staged a smash-and-grab at the Los Alamos nuclear plant late last night,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.86,0:05:27.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and made off with 20 tons of control rods.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.42,0:05:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are the Decepticons looking to build?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.21,0:05:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.86,0:05:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have determined that the synthetic energon formula provided by Knockout is the source of the instability.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Simply because it is incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.47,0:05:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then make haste and complete it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.12,0:05:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not only require enough Cyber-matter to rebuild one planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But to remake a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.94,0:05:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master, excuse my impudence.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.31,0:06:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what is the logic behind ruling two worlds?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has taken me quite some time to fully comprehend
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Earth and Cybertron have always been linked, two halves of one whole,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Primus and Unicron.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that, to rule only one,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would be to never truly rule either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.25,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Cons again In progress this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.41,0:06:31.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coordinates received, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.91,0:06:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's roll!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yip-yip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your ability to roll remains predicated upon further exploration of your manual dexterity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm afraid that Ratchet's authority supersedes my own in medical matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.54,0:06:54.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh... understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.77,0:08:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.98,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ratchet, reopen the groundbridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But ensure that the humans are kept at a safe distance,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For we will be returning with a Decepticon prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we had the foresight to shield our new base
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.81,0:09:02.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,our captive will be unable to transmit his coordinates to the decepticon warship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nor will they, in turn, be able to pinpoint his location.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess we have all the time in the world to make Mr. Personality tell us everything he knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Con's veillance chief must know a lot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Soundwave doesn't speak...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.43,0:09:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure he even has a face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.10,0:09:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Laserbeak unable to triangulate Soundwave's current location,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.69,0:09:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you not concerned about what our comrade might spill?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of one thing, I'm certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.92,0:09:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave knows when to impart information,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.11,0:09:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And when to withhold it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.42,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is Megatron stealing human technology?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.15,0:09:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he attempting to build?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.91,0:09:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wwwhy is MMegatron stealing human ttechnology?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.91,0:09:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wwwhat is he attempting tto build?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Optimus Prime: the remix!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.01,0:10:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah? Why don't I wipe that smile right off his face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.12,0:10:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave, we have treated you fairly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.86,0:10:15.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the sake of the natives of this planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,tell us what Megatron is attempting to build,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.33,0:10:24.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before we are forced to rely upon less civil methods of interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.51,0:10:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scrap this!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.05,0:10:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave is no ordinary Cybertronian, inside or out,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.12,0:10:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I would strongly suggest opening him up
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.05,0:10:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so we can have a first-hand look at the information recorded on his drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.18,0:10:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah-oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.25,0:10:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, he's downloading data.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.55,0:10:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. Soundwave is erasing data.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.29,0:11:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Soundwave superior. Autobots inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.60,0:11:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:19.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His vital signs remain functional.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems he has simply severed all communications,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.07,0:11:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by crashing his own drives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.41,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lord Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.83,0:11:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have located the one item upon this world which possesses
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.80,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,enough raw tonnage to power the reconstructed Omega Lock.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Particle Collider's Synchrotron.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent, Shockwave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.31,0:11:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the successful completion of the synthetic energon formula
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is proving to be far more difficult than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:12:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knockout first procured this unfinished shamble from the Autobot medic,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.73,0:12:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did he not?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my understanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.84,0:12:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then the most efficient means to an end
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.42,0:12:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may very well be to recruit that medic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:13.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attempting to abduct the one Autobot who rarely leaves their base...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:16.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a base we have yet to locate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May prove to be a challenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.05,0:12:24.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You forget that we currently have an agent within the Autobot base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Laserbeak could reconnect with Soundwave,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.03,0:12:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And upload his directive to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.07,0:12:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which would still require knowing the location of their base.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.37,0:12:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is my understanding that Soundwave kept surveillance records of more than just the human children.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prime! These recent Con heists have general bryce breathing down my neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.54,0:12:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I gotta get back to the barbecue today for another grilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.22,0:12:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood, Agent Fowler.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.16,0:12:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And rest assured, should our prisoner return online,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will resume our interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like a plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get back to base as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.96,0:13:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You summoned me, Lord Megatron.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.57,0:13:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I require your services,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.33,0:13:29.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,since we anticipate an Autobot presence at our next event.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.80,0:13:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I welcome any opportunity to face the Prime again,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.55,0:13:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,warrior to warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You pride yourself on your evolution,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet you have learned nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.58,0:13:44.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I may have lost my surveillance chief today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.33,0:13:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Autobots have expanded their forces, while ours continue to dwindle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.27,0:13:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I shall simply battle twice as fiercely.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.96,0:13:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As a beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on my way to the base
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.89,0:14:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I just got word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.60,0:14:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cons busted into the Solaris Particle Collider Project at the south pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.60,0:14:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Autobots.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.85,0:14:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha--? Yip-yip--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.67,0:14:12.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doc, the Commander's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.13,0:14:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Fine, fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:22.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bulkhead, Smokescreen,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.40,0:14:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,remain here with Ratchet to guard our prisoner.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every one else, transform and roll out!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.99,0:14:43.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we throw a tarp over him?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.95,0:14:45.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's creeping me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:47.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It's like he's watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter where you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.08,0:14:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would both of you stop focusing on what Soundwave can or cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.32,0:14:55.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and help me figure out what he did not tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.25,0:15:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like why Megatron would be interested in something believed to generate enough power
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.75,0:15:02.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to create a Black Hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Black holes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.88,0:15:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So Megatron's looking to swallow up the known universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.83,0:15:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And everything in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.43,0:15:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He would merely want to harness the power of something capable of swallowing worlds.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.54,0:15:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to... create one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.33,0:15:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.85,0:15:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Optimus, I know this hardly seems the time... but it may aid you in your task.
